---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Prism AI | AI Automation for Kelowna & Canadian Businesses"
  description="Prism AI helps small and mid-sized businesses in Kelowna and across Canada automate workflows, deploy AI voicebots, and scale operations with practical AI solutions."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Prism AI</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Practical AI automation for Canadian businesses</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-main">
          <h2>Who We Are</h2>
          <p>Prism AI is a Kelowna-based AI automation consultancy founded by Pieter van der Walt. We help small and mid-sized businesses across Canada cut through the noise of AI hype and implement solutions that actually work  saving time, reducing costs, and scaling operations.</p>

          <p>With hands-on experience in AI voicebots, workflow automation, and business process optimization, we focus on delivering measurable results rather than buzzwords. Every solution we build is tailored to your specific business needs and designed to integrate seamlessly with your existing tools and processes.</p>

          <h2>What We Do</h2>
          <p>We specialize in two core areas:</p>

          <div class="service-highlight">
            <h3>AI Voicebots</h3>
            <p>Custom voice AI agents that handle inbound and outbound calls, qualify leads, book appointments, and provide 24/7 customer support  all sounding natural and on-brand for your business.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-highlight">
            <h3>Workflow Automation</h3>
            <p>End-to-end automation of repetitive business processes  from lead follow-up and CRM updates to document processing and team notifications. We connect your existing tools and eliminate manual bottlenecks.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Why Prism AI</h2>
          <p>We are not a faceless enterprise vendor. We are a hands-on team that works directly with business owners to understand their pain points and build solutions that deliver ROI from day one. Based in Kelowna, BC, we understand the unique challenges Canadian SMBs face and price our services accordingly.</p>

          <div class="cta-block">
            <h3>Ready to explore what AI can do for your business?</h3>
            <p>Take our free AI readiness scorecard to see where automation can make the biggest impact.</p>
            <a href="/scorecard" class="btn-primary">Take the Free Scorecard</a>
            <a href="/audit" class="btn-secondary">Learn About Our AI Audit</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .about-content {
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }
  .about-main h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .about-main p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }
  .service-highlight {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid #6c63ff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }
  .service-highlight h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .cta-block {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-block h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .cta-block .btn-primary,
  .cta-block .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cta-block .btn-primary {
    background: #6c63ff;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .cta-block .btn-secondary {
    border: 1px solid #6c63ff;
    color: #6c63ff;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
